@node install "Install? How?

 To install double click on the Install-TB icon.

 TB4.0 now uses Commodore's @{fg shine}installer@{fg text} program because
 it is a very easy to use and time to write a script.

 To install select where you want to install TB and press @{fg shine}Proceed@{fg text}.

 Note:- TB4.0 will not create a drawer, so you will have to create one.

 If you need any help just press the @{fg shine}Help@{fg text} buttons.

 @{" Commodore " link cac}
 @{" Contents  " link Main}

@ENDNODE

